Package: remmm
Type: Package
Title: Resampling-based multivariate mixed model infenrence
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Angela", "Andreella",
      email = "angela.andreella@unive.it",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    ), person("Livio", "Finos", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Fits resampling-based multivariate mixed models for data with within-cluster dependence,
  including multivariate responses, using generalized linear mixed models. The method is described in
  Andreella and Finos (2026).
Imports: flipscores, jointest, MASS, methods
